== Saisatsu Shin's Position == Saisatsu Shin is believed to reside in directions corresponding to the earthy branches (丑, 未, 辰, 戌). Its position depends on the year's {{ill|Chinese zodiac|ja|十二支}}: * Year of the {{ill|Zodiac Sign|ja|十二支}} → Direction of Residence ''' Rat (子) → South-Southwest (未) ''' Ox (丑) → East-Southeast (辰) ''' Tiger (寅) → North-Northeast (丑) ''' Rabbit (卯) → West-Northwest (戌) ''' Dragon (辰) → South-Southwest (未) ''' Snake (巳) → East-Southeast (辰) ''' Horse (午) → North-Northeast (丑) ''' Goat (未) → West-Northwest (戌) ''' Monkey (申) → South-Southwest (未) ''' Rooster (酉) → East-Southeast (辰) ''' Dog (戌) → North-Northeast (丑) ''' Boar (亥) → West-Northwest (戌) == See Also == * {{ill|Guardian Deity of Directions|ja|方位神|1=Directional deity}} * {{ill|Eight Guardian Deities|ja|八将神|1=Eight Directional Deities}}
