[[File:God of Saisatsu.png|thumb|right|170px|Saisatsu Shin]] '''Saisatsu Shin''' (歳殺神, さいせつしん) is one of the {{ill|Eight Guardian Deities|ja|八将神|1=Eight Directional Deities|qq=draft|qq=draft}} in {{ill|Onmyōdō|ja|陰陽道|qq=draft|qq=draft}}. In certain calendars, it may also be written as "さいせつ" (Saisetsu). The {{ill|honji|ja|本地|qq=draft|qq=draft}} in {{ill|Buddhism|ja|仏教|qq=draft|qq=draft}} is identified as {{ill|Yamantaka|ja|大威徳明王|qq=draft|qq=draft}}. It is said to have connections with another of the Eight Guardian Deities, {{ill|Daishōgun (Guardian Deity)|ja|大将軍|1=Daishogun (directional deity)|lt=Daishogun|qq=draft|qq=draft}}.
Saisatsu Shin is associated with {{ill|Venus|ja|金星|qq=draft|qq=draft}}, also known as {{ill|Taihaku|ja|太白星|qq=draft|qq=draft}}. Venus represents the peak of yin energy, and this deity governs destructive energy, believed to annihilate all things. It is advised to avoid actions such as {{ill|moving|ja|引越し|qq=draft|qq=draft}}, {{ill|traveling|ja|旅行|qq=draft|qq=draft}}, {{ill|marriage|ja|結婚|qq=draft|qq=draft}}, or {{ill|lawsuits|ja|訴訟|qq=draft|qq=draft}} in the direction of this deity's presence. However, Saisatsu Shin is said to favor martial matters, and acquiring weapons or blades in its direction is considered auspicious.
== Saisatsu Shin's Position == Saisatsu Shin is believed to reside in directions corresponding to the earthy branches (丑, 未, 辰, 戌). Its position depends on the year's {{ill|Chinese zodiac|ja|十二支|qq=draft|qq=draft}}: * Year of the {{ill|Zodiac Sign|ja|十二支|qq=draft|qq=draft}} → Direction of Residence ''' Rat (子) → South-Southwest (未) ''' Ox (丑) → East-Southeast (辰) ''' Tiger (寅) → North-Northeast (丑) ''' Rabbit (卯) → West-Northwest (戌) ''' Dragon (辰) → South-Southwest (未) ''' Snake (巳) → East-Southeast (辰) ''' Horse (午) → North-Northeast (丑) ''' Goat (未) → West-Northwest (戌) ''' Monkey (申) → South-Southwest (未) ''' Rooster (酉) → East-Southeast (辰) ''' Dog (戌) → North-Northeast (丑) ''' Boar (亥) → West-Northwest (戌) == See Also == * {{ill|Guardian Deity of Directions|ja|方位神|1=Directional deity|1=Directional deity|qq=draft|qq=draft}} * {{ill|Eight Guardian Deities|ja|八将神|1=Eight Directional Deities|qq=draft|qq=draft}}
