<!--Saisetsujin--><!--Saisetsujin--><!--Saisetsujin--><!--Saisetsujin--><!--Saisetsujin--><!--Saisetsujin--><!--Saisetsujin--><!--Saisetsujin--> [[Category:Venusian deities]] <!--jawiki derived wikidata interwikis--> [[zh:歲殺神]]

{{afc comment|Wikidata entry [[d:Q60152]] Wikidata name: Saisetsujin [[User:Immanuelle|Immanuelle]] ([[User talk:Immanuelle|talk]]) 09:01, 11 June 2025 (UTC)}} [[File:God of Saisatsu.png|thumb|right|170px|Saisatsu Shin]] '''Saisatsu Shin''' (歳殺神, さいせつしん) is one of the {{ill|Eight Guardian Deities|ja|八将神|1=Eight Directional Deities|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Eight Guardian Deities|13=User:Immanuelle/Eight Directional Deities|qq=}} in [[:en:Onmyōdō|Onmyōdō]]. In certain calendars, it may also be written as "さいせつ" (Saisetsu). The [[:en:Honji suijaku|Honji]] in [[:en:Buddhism|Buddhism]] is identified as [[:en:Yamantaka|Yamantaka]]. It is said to have connections with another of the Eight Guardian Deities, {{ill|Daishōgun (Guardian Deity)|ja|大将軍|1=Daishōgun (directional deity)|lt=Daishōgun|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Daishōgun (Guardian Deity)|13=User:Immanuelle/Daishōgun (directional deity)|qq=}}.
Saisatsu Shin is associated with [[:en:Venus|Venus]], also known as {{ill|Taihaku|ja|太白星|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Taihaku|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 金星}}. Venus represents the peak of yin energy, and this deity governs destructive energy, believed to annihilate all things. It is advised to avoid actions such as [[:en:Relocation (personal)|moving]], [[:en:Travel|traveling]], [[:en:Marriage|marriage]], or [[:en:Legal proceeding|lawsuits]] in the direction of this deity's presence. However, Saisatsu Shin is said to favor martial matters, and acquiring weapons or blades in its direction is considered auspicious.
== Saisatsu Shin's Position == Saisatsu Shin is believed to reside in directions corresponding to the earthy branches (丑, 未, 辰, 戌). Its position depends on the year's [[:en:Earthly Branches|Chinese zodiac]]: * Year of the [[:en:Earthly Branches|Zodiac Sign]] → Direction of Residence ''' Rat (子) → South-Southwest (未) ''' Ox (丑) → East-Southeast (辰) ''' Tiger (寅) → North-Northeast (丑) ''' Rabbit (卯) → West-Northwest (戌) ''' Dragon (辰) → South-Southwest (未) ''' Snake (巳) → East-Southeast (辰) ''' Horse (午) → North-Northeast (丑) ''' Goat (未) → West-Northwest (戌) ''' Monkey (申) → South-Southwest (未) ''' Rooster (酉) → East-Southeast (辰) ''' Dog (戌) → North-Northeast (丑) ''' Boar (亥) → West-Northwest (戌) == See Also == * {{ill|Guardian Deity of Directions|ja|方位神|1=Directional deity|1=Directional deity|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Guardian Deity of Directions|13=User:Immanuelle/Directional deity|qq=}} * {{ill|Eight Guardian Deities|ja|八将神|1=Eight Directional Deities|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Eight Guardian Deities|13=User:Immanuelle/Eight Directional Deities|qq=}}
